      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meriden%2C_Connecticut"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Meriden Historical Society’s Museum & History Center, located at 41 West Main Street, preserves the town’s industrial and cultural heritage.",
