      ],
      "source": "https://meridenhistoricalsociety.org/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Both the Quinnipiac River Gorge Trail and the Hanover Pond Trail trace the abandoned Meriden, Waterbury and Connecticut River Railroad bed.",
